metadata.description: Tomi Pomo is an Argentine art director, visual artist, tattooist and designer. He has built a reputation as one of the most prestigious tattoo artists in Buenos Aires, leaving traces of his masterful lines in several top tier studios in the capital, such as the niche Local Support. The rise of Tomi to the top of Argentina's contemporary art scene was built consistently over the last decade, as he introduced his tradermark characters into the cityscape.
